{{champion:9}} 
Been playing Middlesticks a lot recently. They recently lowered his CD on E too, the spell you max first in lane. Basically you spam E on the caster minions, it's free poke if it bounces to the laner, and waveclear too. Once you hit 6, go into the bottom side brush as though you're roaming bot. Usually the enemy will finish clearing the wave then try to either follow your "roam", or at least go to ward the bush you're in. When he does this, ult out at them and it's usually a free kill. Start Morello into Zhonya's, then whatever you want after. 
He's great against most mages, and assassins too thanks to his silence and fear. And draining the cannon minion is some nice sustain as well.

